text: Admete frigida is a species of sea snail, a marine gastropod mollusk in the family Cancellariidae, the nutmeg snails. ==Description== The shell grows to a length of 7 mm. ==Distribution== This marine species occurs in the Magellanic Straits. ==References== ==External links== * Rochebrune A.-T. de & Mabille J.
